name: James Pond II - Codename - Robocod [SG]
description:
James Pond 2: Codename Robocod is an arcade game developed by Millennium Interactive, Millenium Interactive and Vectordean. It came out on 01-01-1993. Electronic Arts published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Meh".
James Pond 2: Codename Robocod is available on PC, Atari ST, Game Gear and SEGA Master System.
Richard Joseph scored the game.
